marketing: Shell Spirax S5 ADE 75W-85 is a premium performance, fuel economy, extreme-pressure axle oil based on synthetic technology. It is designed with containing multi-functional additives which impart excellent anti-wear properties, oxidation stability and anti-rust characteristics. It is suitable for gear applications presenting load- speed conditions of extreme severity, such as medium and low speed spur or helical gear units, spiral-bevel and hypoid axle units as well as extended drain capabilities. It is designed and approved for use in application requiring Mercedes Benz 235.31.
